msgid "The `io.quarkus.vertx.http.security.HttpSecurity` CDI event allows to configure the Basic authentication mechanism programmatically like in the example below:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-basic-authentication.adoc
msgid "Enable the Basic authentication and use the `QuarkusTestRealm` authentication realm."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-basic-authentication.adoc
msgid "If you generate an OpenAPI schema document with the SmallRye OpenAPI extension, the Basic authentication must be enabled during the build-time with the `quarkus.http.auth.basic` configuration property."
msgstr ""

